{"tid":1708170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日行動，少少意見，唔知work唔work。","createTime":"2019-11-11T13:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T13:37:16.000Z","uid":311492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3f6db15325ee432f04768c05e195a4b46b0e41f8","tid":1708170,"uid":311492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:25:29.000Z","msg":"手足可以一齊試下落樓下最近個條大路堵塞。一個屋苑點都有一百幾十人出黎嘅。唔洗特定去某啲地方堵路。<br />\n第一，方便安全，落樓下堵完，有咩事就返屋企，班狗走左再塞過。<br />\n第二，範圍大難清理，每區都有唔少屋苑，只要一齊落樓下堵路成效已經好好，而且範圍大，未必有足夠嘅鬼mon住我地。而且更分散。<br />\n另外，尤其有巴士總站個啲，塞住樓下個巴士站已經無車出到。<br />\n第三，屋苑一定有藍絲，到時夠手足私了就可以。而且對家難佈處。"},{"pid":"46460768580acaf51ca5f0098d38c16499652326","tid":1708170,"uid":311492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6d53c957d00dd8f692d8940370c376c0f62503ad","tid":1708170,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:37:16.000Z","msg":"roadblock 要升級，要夠大唔易清啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCOr7Eo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCOr7Eo.jpg&h=e467864d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>朝早係春袋，阻人返工點得架？！<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"><br />\n全民早起，繼續三罷，癱瘓交通，攬炒經濟！<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxBpTKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxBpTKS.jpg&h=b20fd793&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}